\par \'93Weal\'94 (if the action will probably bring good results).
\par \'93Woe\'94 (for bad results).
\par \'93Weal and woe\'94 (for both).
\par \'93Nothing\'94 (for actions that don\rquote t have especially good or bad results).
\par If the spell fails, the caster gets the \'93nothing\'94 result. A divine caster who gets the \'93nothing\'94 result has no way to tell whether it was the consequence of a failed or successful }{\cs27\fs20 augury}{\fs20 .
