s holding, chooses its path randomly (as long as it is getting away from immediate danger), and flees any other dangers that confront it. If cornered, a 
panicked creature cowers. A cowering creature loses its Dexterity bonus, can take no actions, and takes a \endash 2 penalty to its Defense.
