\par The }{\cs27\fs20 knock}{\fs20  spell opens stuck, barred, locked, or magically held or sealed doors. It opens secret doors, as well as locked or trick-openi
ng boxes or chests. It also loosens welds, shackles, or chains (provided they serve to hold closures shut). In all other cases, the door does not relock itself or become stuck again on its own. }{\cs27\fs20 Knock}{\fs20 
 does not raise barred gates or similar impediments, nor does it affect ropes, vines, and the like. Note that the effect is limited by the area.  Each spell can undo up to two means of preventing egress. 
\par 
