Saving Throw:}{\fs20  None; }{\b\fs20 Spell Resistance:}{\fs20  No
\par A }{\cs27\fs20 wall of force}{\fs20  spell creates an invisible wall of force. The }{\cs27\fs20 wall of force}{\fs20  cannot move, it is immune to damage of all kinds, and it is unaffected by }{\cs27\fs20 dispel magic}{\fs20 
. Spells, breath weapons, and flamethrowers cannot pass through the wall in either direction, although }{\cs27\fs20 dimension door}{\fs20  can bypass the barrier. Gaze attacks can operate through the }{\cs27\fs20 wall of force}{\fs20 .
\par The caster can form the wall into a flat, vertical plane whose area is up to one 10-foot square per level, or into a sphere or hemisphere with a radius of up to 1 foot per level.
\par The }{\cs27\fs20 wall of force}{\fs20  must be continuous and unbroken when formed. If its surface is broken by any object or creature, the spell fails.
\par 
